definition: to get rid of/to remove/to exclude/to eliminate/to wipe out/to divide/except/not including
(completed action marker)/(modal particle indicating change of state, situation now)/(modal particle intensifying preceding clause)
to finish/to achieve/variant of 瞭|了[liao3]/to understand clearly

sentences.english: Beyond that gunshot there’s no evidence.
sentences.chinese: 除了枪声之外，就没有任何证据了。

sentences.english: There was a moment of silence, then everyone but the Princess began to laugh.
sentences.chinese: 片刻寂静之后，皇族贵胄们哄堂大笑，除了公主。

sentences.english: Despite the clouds, the Matterhorn still was a great piece of rock to look at.
sentences.chinese: 除了云朵外，马特宏峰看上去始终是块壮观的石头。

sentences.english: I can resist everything except temptation" is a very interesting epigram ."
sentences.chinese: “除了诱惑我什么都能够抵制”是句非常有趣的隽语。

sentences.english: The walls were bare except for a clock.
sentences.chinese: 墙上除了一只挂钟什么也没有。

sentences.english: Weekly con calls will be setup to monitor progress along with documentation of deliverables.
sentences.chinese: 除了交付的文件，每周还要举行电话会谈以监督进程。

sentences.english: Besides lacking in hygiene, some lack common sense as well.
sentences.chinese: 有些女生除了没有清洁意识之外，还缺乏基本常识。

sentences.english: It's easier to drink with no fishy taste .
sentences.chinese: 去除了鱼类原有的鱼腥味，变得更为容易饮用。

sentences.english: "Other than pedophilia, it's the most secretive behavior I've encountered, " says Charles Yesalis, a Penn State University professor who has studied steroid use for 28 years.
sentences.chinese: 除了恋童癖外，这是我遇到过最秘密的行为了。

sentences.english: Except whenbeing interviewed at D with Bill Gates.
sentences.chinese: 除了和盖茨同台被采访的时候。

sentences.english: After the US, no other country has so many people in this list.
sentences.chinese: 除了美国以外，没有其它国家有如此多的富豪入围。

sentences.english: What do you think it takes to beat you besides luck?
sentences.chinese: 你觉得要想打败你，除了运气还需要点什么？
除了美德，一切须有节制。

sentences.english: There’s still nothing much to do here, just watch TV or help with chores.
sentences.chinese: 在这里仍然无事可做，除了看电视和帮忙做家务。

sentences.english: I had noting in the world but a million-pound note.
sentences.chinese: 除了一张百万英磅的钞票外，我一无所有。

sentences.english: Besides, a significant part of the business sector is highly levered .
sentences.chinese: 除了商业部门的有效部分会使用高杠杆。
